Great.

283
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:41,560
Where the hell is this place?

284
00:20:45,230 --> 00:20:47,560
Xifeng Lie. Xifeng Lie.

285
00:20:47,560 --> 00:20:48,960
Xifeng Lie.

286
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:52,360
