287
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:55,360
Miss Xia, why did you capture me?

288
00:20:56,360 --> 00:21:00,360
Lord Shang, why couldn't I capture you?

289
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,300
You know who I am.

290
00:21:02,300 --> 00:21:03,700
Who the hell are you?

291
00:21:07,230 --> 00:21:09,630
Shang Yu. Xifeng Lie.

292
00:21:09,630 --> 00:21:10,560
I've come to your rescue.

293
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:11,960
Prince Tang.

294
00:21:12,630 --> 00:21:14,500
You messed with the wrong people today.

295
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:16,230
I'm Bei Tangtang, or Prince Tang,

296
