a member of Pisces, the Beitang Family

297
00:21:17,630 --> 00:21:19,760
from the Zodiac State.

298
00:21:19,760 --> 00:21:21,630
If you're clever, you should put down your weapons.

299
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,230
What did he say?

300
00:21:24,030 --> 00:21:25,960
Leave when I'm not furious,

301
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:27,500
and I'll spare your lives

302
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:29,360
for the sake of

303
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:30,630
the God.

304
00:22:04,630 --> 00:22:05,430
Take him away.

305
00:22:11,430 --> 00:22:14,030
Your Highness, why are you here?

306
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:15,360
